ul.li: Coordinators can add/edit EP data in the GPM.
The GPM either sends a message to the data exchange or directly messages the affiliations service API.
The affiliations service updates its database according to the Kafka or API message.
The GCI/VCI uses the affiliations service API to get data about affiliations, so it is always up-to-date.
The GCI/VCI can register users and send user data to the GPM via the data exchange.
